<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/home.css"> <!-- Link to the external CSS file -->
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Welcome to the Automated Timetable Generation System</h1>
            <% if (user) { %>
                <p class="greeting"><b>Hello, <%= user.username %></b></p>
            <% } else { %>
                <p class="greeting">Please log in to access your timetable.</p>
            <% } %>
        </header>

    
        <!-- Button group for core features -->
        <div class="button-group">
            <form action="/" method="GET">
                <button class="main-btn" type="submit">View Timetable</button>
            </form>
            <form action="/addTeacher" method="GET">
                <button class="main-btn" type="submit">Add Teacher</button>
            </form>
            <form action="/addSubject" method="GET">
                <button class="main-btn" type="submit">Add Subject</button>
            </form>
        </div>

         <!-- Informational section -->
         <div class="info-section">
                            <h2>About the System</h2>
                <p>The College Timetable System streamlines the management of teachers, subjects, and schedules. It enables you to effortlessly add new instructors, define course subjects, and organize or review timetables for the semester.</p>
                <p>Use the navigation buttons above to explore the features and efficiently manage your academic data.</p>

        </div>
        

        <!-- Logout link -->
        <a href="/logout" class="logout-link">Logout</a>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 College Timetable System. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
